{
  "texts": [
    "In our paper, we also anticipate the emergence of advanced human-AI integration paradigms, such as neural integration, emphasizing HRM's role in ensuring ethical, responsible, and fair practices.",
    "By looking at the issue from culture, compliance, and people management, our framework not only paves a roadmap toward human-centric AI, but also distinguishes organizations as stewards of technology that enhances, rather than diminishes, the human experience and potential.",
    "The paper serves as a forward-looking guide for HRM practitioners, policymakers, and researchers seeking to navigate the transformative landscape of AI in HRM while upholding ethical principles and fostering a future where AI and humans symbiotically co-exist in the workplace.",
    "Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence frontiersin.org"
  ]
}